ComicInfo.Title: The Glorious Return of Sweet Baby Theda; Orphee, Poor Orphee, They Made Him in a Jar Right There in the Lab!
ComicInfo.Summary:
The Glorious Return of Sweet Baby Theda: Vampirella and Pantha are hired by a former child star who wants to make a comeback movie.
Orphee, Poor Orphee, They Made Him in a Jar Right There in the Lab!: Vampirella's first movie job is interrupted by a genetically engineered monster.
